result.title: Martin Scorsese Directs
result.overview: Providing behind the scenes footage of the director on set with clips from his own films, Martin Scorsese Directs depicts to riveting effect the way Scorsese brings the written story to life on the big screen. Additional interviews with the likes of Joe Pesci, Harvey Keitel, Thelma Schoonmaker, the director’s own parents, and others build a perception of Scorsese that not everybody knows.

result.title: Happy Birthday Switzerland
result.overview: A wry, satirical look celebration of 700 years of Switzerland and Swiss culture.
